{"segment":13,"line_start":346,"line_end":370,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_da_biao_ju_qing_yi","text":"\"你们看清楚，老子就是朱猛。\"","tone":"大笑","chapter":2,"line_start":348,"line_end":348},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_da_biao_ju_qing_yi","text":"\"老子留下你们的脑袋，只因为老子要你们用眼睛把老夫看清楚，用嘴巴回去告诉司马和卓东来，老子已经来过了。\"","tone":"豪迈","chapter":2,"line_start":348,"line_end":352},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_da_biao_ju_qing_yi","text":"\"你们还不快滚？\"","tone":"厉声","chapter":2,"line_start":354,"line_end":354},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"现在我才知道，这个世界上像孙通那么不怕死的人实在不多。\"","tone":"无奈","chapter":2,"line_start":358,"line_end":360}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":14,"line_start":372,"line_end":406,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_xiao_gao","text":"\"你在干什么？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":378,"line_end":378},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"我在喝茶，\"","tone":"平静","chapter":2,"line_start":380,"line_end":380},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"我口渴，想喝茶。\"","tone":"平静","chapter":2,"line_start":380,"line_end":380},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_xiao_gao","text":"\"可是你没有喝。\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":382,"line_end":382},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"因为茶已经冷了，\"","tone":"平静","chapter":2,"line_start":384,"line_end":384},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"我一向不喜欢喝冷茶。\"","tone":"平静","chapter":2,"line_start":384,"line_end":384},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"喝酒我不在乎，什么样的酒我都喝，可是，喝茶我一向很讲究，冷茶是万万喝不得的，要我喝冷茶，我宁可喝毒酒。\"","tone":"认真","chapter":2,"line_start":386,"line_end":388},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_xiao_gao","text":"\"难道你还想从这个茶壶里倒杯热茶出来？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":390,"line_end":390},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"我本来就在这么想。\"","tone":"平静","chapter":2,"line_start":392,"line_end":392},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_xiao_gao","text":"\"你知不知道这壶茶已经完全冷了？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":394,"line_end":394},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"我知道，\"","tone":"平静","chapter":2,"line_start":396,"line_end":396},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"我当然知道。\"","tone":"平静","chapter":2,"line_start":396,"line_end":396},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_xiao_gao","text":"\"你知道这壶茶已经冷了，可是你还想从这壶茶里倒杯热的出来。\"","tone":"惊讶","chapter":2,"line_start":398,"line_end":400},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"不但要热的，而且还要烫。\"","tone":"平静","chapter":2,"line_start":402,"line_end":402},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"又滚又热的茶才好喝。\"","tone":"平静","chapter":2,"line_start":402,"line_end":402},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_ding_xie","text":"\"我本来想把这小子的脑袋砍下来的，可是我现在不能砍了，\"","tone":"大笑","chapter":2,"line_start":404,"line_end":404},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_ding_xie","text":"\"这小子是个疯子，老子从来不砍疯子的脑袋。\"","tone":"大笑","chapter":2,"line_start":404,"line_end":406}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[{"type":"内功","faction":"无","rank":"出神入化","progression":["本章首次显露"],"effects":[{"type":"特殊","description":"证明内力深厚并扭转朱猛判断"}],"rag_refs":["ch_002:390-414"],"source_refs":[{"chapter":2,"line_start":390,"line_end":414,"text":"\"难道你还想从这个茶壶里倒杯热茶出来？\"朱猛问小高。\n\"我本来就在这么想。\"\n\"你知不知道这壶茶已经完全冷了？\"\n\"我知道，\"小高说，\"我当然知道。\"\n朱猛看着他，就好像看着个怪物一样：\"你知道这壶茶已经冷了，可是你还想从这壶茶里倒杯热的出"}],"id":"skill_nei_li_re_cha","name":"内力热茶","one_line":"小高以掌心内力将冷茶逼热，显露深厚内功。","techniques":[{"id":"tech_zhang_xin_cui_re","name":"掌心催热","type":"special","description":"以掌心内力和热力贯入茶壶，使冷茶变成滚烫热茶。"},{"id":"tech_leng_cha_bian_re","name":"冷茶变热","type":"special","description":"不动声色地从冷壶中倒出热茶，用奇异内功震住朱猛。"}],"combat_style":"含蓄奇诡，以日常动作展示内力。","ls":390,"le":414}],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":15,"line_start":408,"line_end":432,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_ding_xie","text":"\"这小子是不是疯子？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":416,"line_end":416},{"speaker":"char_ding_xie","speaker_name":"钉鞋","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"好像不是。\"","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":418,"line_end":418},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_ding_xie","text":"\"这小子是不是好像还有他娘的一点真功夫？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":420,"line_end":420},{"speaker":"char_ding_xie","speaker_name":"钉鞋","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"好像是的。\"","tone":"陈述","chapter":2,"line_start":422,"line_end":422},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_ding_xie","text":"\"想不到这小子还真是好小子。\"","tone":"欣喜","chapter":2,"line_start":424,"line_end":424},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_ding_xie","text":"\"老子居然差一点看走眼了。\"","tone":"欣喜","chapter":2,"line_start":424,"line_end":426},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_xiao_gao","text":"\"你不是疯子，你是条好汉，只要你肯认我做兄弟，肯陪我回去痛痛快快地喝几天酒，我马上就跪下来给你磕三个响头。\"","tone":"认真","chapter":2,"line_start":428,"line_end":430}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[{"type":"special","source_skill":"skill_nei_li_re_cha","effects":[],"related_characters":["char_xiao_gao"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":["ch_002:410-414"],"source_refs":[{"chapter":2,"line_start":410,"line_end":414,"text":"他看见小高居然真的从那壶冷茶里，倒了一杯热的出来，滚烫的热茶，烫得冒烟。\n朱猛的笑声也很快就停顿，因为他也看见了这件事。\n看见这种事之后还能够笑得出来的人并不多。能够用掌心的内力和热力，把一壶冷茶变成热茶的人也不多。"}],"id":"tech_zhang_xin_cui_re","name":"掌心催热","description":"小高用掌心内力和热力使一壶冷茶变成滚烫热茶。","ls":410,"le":414},{"type":"special","source_skill":"skill_nei_li_re_cha","effects":[],"related_characters":["char_xiao_gao"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":["ch_002:410-414"],"source_refs":[{"chapter":2,"line_start":410,"line_end":414,"text":"他看见小高居然真的从那壶冷茶里，倒了一杯热的出来，滚烫的热茶，烫得冒烟。\n朱猛的笑声也很快就停顿，因为他也看见了这件事。\n看见这种事之后还能够笑得出来的人并不多。能够用掌心的内力和热力，把一壶冷茶变成热茶的人也不多。"}],"id":"tech_leng_cha_bian_re","name":"冷茶变热","description":"小高从已冷的茶壶里倒出冒烟热茶，令朱猛和钉鞋都无法再发笑。","ls":410,"le":414}],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_xiao_gao","attribute_updates":{"name":"高渐飞"}}]}
{"segment":16,"line_start":434,"line_end":460,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"现在我才相信江湖中人说的不假，雄狮朱猛果然是个了不起的角色，难怪有那么多人服你，肯为你去卖命了。\"","tone":"苦笑","chapter":2,"line_start":436,"line_end":438},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_xiao_gao","text":"\"你呢？\"","tone":"焦急","chapter":2,"line_start":440,"line_end":440},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_xiao_gao","text":"\"你肯不肯交我朱猛这个朋友？\"","tone":"焦急","chapter":2,"line_start":440,"line_end":440},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"他奶奶的，交朋友就交朋友，交个朋友有什么了不起。\"","tone":"豪迈","chapter":2,"line_start":442,"line_end":444},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"我高渐飞在江湖中混了几个月，还没有遇到过一个像你这么样看得起我的人，我为什么不能交你这个朋友？\"","tone":"豪迈","chapter":2,"line_start":444,"line_end":446},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_xiao_gao","text":"\"好！说得好！\"","tone":"欣喜","chapter":2,"line_start":448,"line_end":448},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"只不过磕头这件事千万要免掉。\"","tone":"调侃","chapter":2,"line_start":450,"line_end":450},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"你给我跪下来，我也不能站着，若是两个人全跪在地上磕头，你磕过来，我磕过去，岂非变成一对磕头虫了？\"","tone":"调侃","chapter":2,"line_start":450,"line_end":452},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"这种事我是绝不做的。\"","tone":"认真","chapter":2,"line_start":454,"line_end":454},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_xiao_gao","text":"\"你说不做，咱们就不做。\"","tone":"欣喜","chapter":2,"line_start":458,"line_end":458},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"我也不能陪你回去喝酒，\"","tone":"无奈","chapter":2,"line_start":460,"line_end":460},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"我在长安还有个死约会。\"","tone":"认真","chapter":2,"line_start":460,"line_end":460}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":17,"line_start":462,"line_end":488,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_xiao_gao","text":"\"那么咱们就在这里喝，喝他个痛快。\"","tone":"豪迈","chapter":2,"line_start":462,"line_end":462},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"就在这里喝？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":464,"line_end":464},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"你不怕司马赶来？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":464,"line_end":464},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_xiao_gao","text":"\"他奶奶的，就算他来了又有什么了不起？老子最多也只不过把这条命去跟他拼掉而已，他还能把老子怎么样？\"","tone":"豪迈","chapter":2,"line_start":468,"line_end":470},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_xiao_gao","text":"\"可是咱们这顿酒却是非喝不可的，不喝比死还难受。\"","tone":"豪迈","chapter":2,"line_start":470,"line_end":472},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"好！喝就喝，\"","tone":"豪迈","chapter":2,"line_start":474,"line_end":474},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"要是你不怕，我怕个鸟。\"","tone":"豪迈","chapter":2,"line_start":474,"line_end":474},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_xiao_gao","text":"\"我再敬你三大碗。\"","tone":"豪迈","chapter":2,"line_start":488,"line_end":488},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_xiao_gao","text":"\"祝你多福多寿，身子健康。\"","tone":"豪迈","chapter":2,"line_start":488,"line_end":488}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":18,"line_start":490,"line_end":516,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"好！我喝。\"","tone":"豪迈","chapter":2,"line_start":490,"line_end":490},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_xiao_gao","text":"\"这次轮到你敬我了。\"","tone":"豪迈","chapter":2,"line_start":496,"line_end":496},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_xiao_gao","text":"\"你最少也得敬我三大碗。\"","tone":"豪迈","chapter":2,"line_start":496,"line_end":496},{"speaker":"char_ding_xie","speaker_name":"钉鞋","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"报告堂主，这三碗恐怕是不能再喝了。\"","tone":"担心","chapter":2,"line_start":498,"line_end":498},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_ding_xie","text":"\"为什么？为什么不能喝？\"","tone":"愤怒","chapter":2,"line_start":500,"line_end":500},{"speaker":"char_ding_xie","speaker_name":"钉鞋","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"报告堂主，再喝下去，这位高少爷的性命恐怕也要陪堂主一起拼掉。\"","tone":"担心","chapter":2,"line_start":502,"line_end":504},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_xiao_gao","text":"\"他说的也有理，我的性命拼掉无妨，为什么要连累你？\"","tone":"无奈","chapter":2,"line_start":504,"line_end":506},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"我的命又不比你值钱，你能拼命，我为什么不能？\"","tone":"平静","chapter":2,"line_start":508,"line_end":508},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"何况我们也未必就拼不过他们。\"","tone":"豪迈","chapter":2,"line_start":510,"line_end":510},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_xiao_gao","text":"\"有理，你说得更有理。\"","tone":"大笑","chapter":2,"line_start":510,"line_end":512},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"所以我也要敬你三大碗，也祝你多福多寿，身子健康。\"","tone":"豪迈","chapter":2,"line_start":514,"line_end":514}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":19,"line_start":518,"line_end":546,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ding_xie","speaker_name":"钉鞋","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"报告堂主，现在我也想喝点酒了。\"","tone":"苦笑","chapter":2,"line_start":522,"line_end":524},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"我还要再敬你三大碗，\"","tone":"豪迈","chapter":2,"line_start":542,"line_end":542},{"speaker":"char_xiao_gao","speaker_name":"小高","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"这三碗祝你长命富贵，多子多孙。\"","tone":"豪迈","chapter":2,"line_start":542,"line_end":544},{"speaker":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","speaker_name":"卓东来","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"这三大碗应该由我来敬了。\"","tone":"淡然","chapter":2,"line_start":544,"line_end":546}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":20,"line_start":548,"line_end":586,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","text":"\"为什么？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":548,"line_end":548},{"speaker":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","speaker_name":"卓东来","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"朱堂主远来，我们居然完全没有尽到一点地主之谊，这三碗当然应该由我来敬。\"","tone":"淡然","chapter":2,"line_start":550,"line_end":552},{"speaker":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","speaker_name":"卓东来","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"我也还要再敬朱堂主三大碗。\"","tone":"淡然","chapter":2,"line_start":556,"line_end":556},{"speaker":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","speaker_name":"卓东来","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"这三碗酒我也是非喝不可的。\"","tone":"淡然","chapter":2,"line_start":556,"line_end":558},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","text":"\"为什么？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":560,"line_end":560},{"speaker":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","speaker_name":"卓东来","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"因为喝过这三碗酒之后，我就有件事想请教朱堂主了。\"","tone":"淡然","chapter":2,"line_start":562,"line_end":562},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","text":"\"什么事？\"","tone":"疑问","chapter":2,"line_start":564,"line_end":564},{"speaker":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","speaker_name":"卓东来","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"朱堂主行踪飘忽，神出鬼没，把这里视若无人之地。\"","tone":"认真","chapter":2,"line_start":566,"line_end":566},{"speaker":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","speaker_name":"卓东来","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"如果朱堂主刚才就走了，我们也实在无能为力。\"","tone":"无奈","chapter":2,"line_start":568,"line_end":568},{"speaker":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","speaker_name":"卓东来","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"可是朱堂主刚才为什么不走呢？\"","tone":"冷酷","chapter":2,"line_start":570,"line_end":572},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","text":"\"你想不到？\"","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":2,"line_start":574,"line_end":574},{"speaker":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","speaker_name":"卓东来","listener":"char_zhu_meng","text":"\"我实在想不到！\"","tone":"认真","chapter":2,"line_start":576,"line_end":576},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","text":"\"其实我本来也没有想到，因为那时我还没有交到这个朋友。\"","tone":"豪迈","chapter":2,"line_start":578,"line_end":580},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","text":"\"现在我既然已经交了这个朋友，我当然要陪他喝几杯。\n他既然不能跟我回去，我也只好留在这里陪他。\"","tone":"豪迈","chapter":2,"line_start":580,"line_end":582},{"speaker":"char_zhu_meng","speaker_name":"朱猛","listener":"char_zhuo_dong_lai","text":"\"这道理其实简单得很，只可惜你们这样的人绝对不会明白而已。\"","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":2,"line_start":584,"line_end":586}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
